Key Match Events: Devin Booker and Jaren Jackson Jr. react during the fourth quarter of the game at Footprint Center.
Pre-Game Insights: The Suns are 15-17 entering the 2025 calendar year, a massive letdown considering what the team was supposed to be.

Others: Phoenix is back in action on Saturday against the Indiana Pacers.
